        <text textAlign="center">Table 55: Technology Use, Systems TN and Time</text>
        <text><b>Special</b></text>
        <text>   A character can take 10 when using the Technology Use skill.
        </text>
        <text><b>Time</b></text>
        <text>   Technology Use requires 12 CP. The GM may determine that some tasks require several rounds, a few minutes, or longer, as described above.
